JM, 9/6/93
	Added compilation flag NOALLOCA, for systems that don't have alloca.
	Altered gdbmopen.c, gdbmfetch.c and falloc.c so that they use the
	macro ALLOCA_FREE to free the storage on these systems.

JM, 25/5/93
	Added pop_gdbm.c and mkgdbm.
	Changes systems.h to remove use of flock
	Removed files for ndbm and dbm. Removed test files.
